Product Description

Make your better half feel special with this perfume by Paco Rabanne. This perfume comes in a beautiful crystal bottle in purple colour adorned with a rose on it. This bottle will definitely give you a feeling of a princess. Gelled with top notes of cranberry pink peppercorn and tamarind this perfume is designed for daily wear. Its middle notes are dressed with a flavour of Hellebore noir rose black violet and cocoa blossom. Its bottom notes are gelled with patchouli massoia wood and vanilla. It is for the confident contemporary women of today. Paco Rabanne Black XS for Her Eau de Toilette contains enchanting ingredients which radiate at the top with the audacious and cheerful tamarind flower. You can make your evenings even more romantic and sexy with this Paco Rabanne Black Xs perfume.

column17:
Product Description

The house of Paco Rabanne's fragrance for men is announced as a fresh and sensual blend of notes with glittery shine of gold for which creator Paco Rabanne says the following: "In all civilizations and religions gold has always managed to seduce people". Gold is all around us: In architecture design jewelry clothes accessories fashion it is noticeable and respected worldwide and it possesses divine notes. The bottle of this edition for men is created in golden nuances. The perfume was inspired by Paco Rabanne's metallic fashion and created in cooperation with three famous noses for perfumes Christophe Raynaud Olivier Pescheux and Michel Girard who mixed this year's edition from the notes of sparkling grapefruit red orange mint rose cinnamon spices blond leather blond wood patchouli and amber. The perfume is available in the amount of 50 and 100 ml as an edp and with accompanying body care products. The package is very luxurious made of golden body with a diamond crown. Each bottle is separately numerated and the edition is limited. The outer package - a case that holds a golden lever is created by Noe Duchaufour-Lawrence. Let us remind you of the fragrant composition: The perfumers behind it are Christopher Raynaud Olivier Pescheux and Michel Girard and the notes are: Sexy blood orange grapefruit cinnamon mint rose spices light leather white wood patchouli and amber.
